== Autonomic Dysfunction
<sec:autonomic>

Autonomic dysfunction is present in 70–90% of ME/CFS patients @Newton2007autonomicDysfunction, manifesting as ortho\-static in\-tolerance, temperature dys\-regulation, and cardio\-vascular symptoms.

